# ma-chaton

This is simple archive I started something, but didn't have enought time to proceed. 

## Agenda

When I configured some services suricata or firewall I would like to test if it is
operational.

## What to build

- Must read file
    - need lib to read file, must be robust and reliable
    - Errors: path do not exists, file is unreadable, permission denied, file is empty.
- Must take params at start
    - patch of file (relative)
    - help
    - version
- Must have help
- Must be async
- Must have readable error messages

